Package org.bukkit.block.data.type

Interface Scaffolding

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlockData, java.lang.Cloneable, Waterlogged
    public interface Scaffolding
extends Waterlogged
    'bottom' indicates whether the scaffolding is floating or not.
    'distance' indicates the distance from a scaffolding block placed above a 'bottom' scaffold.
    When 'distance' reaches getMaximumDistance() the block will drop.
